<docbook><section><title>ODSProfileManagerGuide</title><title>ODS Profile Manager Usage Guide</title>ODS Profile Manager Usage Guide
<para>The following guide shows how to manage your ODS User Profile.</para>
<para> </para>
<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2"> Accessing the ODS Profile Manager</bridgehead>
<para>A logged-in user may access the ODS Profile Manager at any time through the link at the top of the page.</para>
<orderedlist spacing="compact"><listitem>Visit an ODS instance with your Web browser, &lt;<ulink url="http://host:port/ods">http://host:port/ods</ulink>&gt;, such as <ulink url="http://my.openlinksw.com/ods">http://my.openlinksw.com/ods</ulink>.
</listitem>
<listitem>Log in or register as an ODS user.
 (If you have ever registered with or downloaded from OpenLink Software, you have an existing account which uses your email address as the username.
 You can <ulink url="http://download.openlinksw.com:8080/download/register.vsp?hname=http://download.openlinksw.com:8080/download/main_login.vsp&amp;nhdr=">register now or get a password reminder</ulink>, if needed.) <figure><graphic fileref="ODSProfileManagerGuide/p1.png" /></figure> </listitem>
<listitem>Successful log-in and/or registration will bring you to the ODS user home page.
<figure><graphic fileref="ODSProfileManagerGuide/p2.png" /></figure> </listitem>
<listitem>Click the <emphasis>Edit</emphasis> link (next to, but not the same as, the <emphasis>Profile</emphasis> link) in the header bar, to access the ODS Profile Manager.
<figure><graphic fileref="ODSProfileManagerGuide/p3.png" /></figure></listitem>
